	<h2>Artistic Practice</h2>
	<p>
		Sool Park is a poet and literary translator working between Korean and German. His own writing
		appears with Achimdal (Seoul) and in journals such as <em>Modern Poetics</em>, <em>Krachkultur</em>
		and <em>Lowland Art Magazine</em>; his translations appear with S. Fischer, Itta, Karl Alber and
		Pungwoldang.
	</p>

